des: To hear information about Topeka Kansas ask Alexa to open Topeka Kansas Facts. Alexa will then tell you some information about the Capitol city of Kansas. Information for this skill was gathered from the Topeka Shawnee County Public Library, various web sites, information from Warde Meade Park and other local areas.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
